ca.usask.simlab.odeToJava.scheme

Class ERKButcherTableau

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.usask.simlab.odeToJava.scheme.Scheme
      • ca.usask.simlab.odeToJava.scheme.ERKButcherTableau

  • public class ERKButcherTableau
extends Scheme
    This class holds information about a single explicit Runge-Kutta scheme in the form of a Butcher tableau.

    Ernst Hairer, Syvert Norsett, and Gerhard Wanner. "Solving Order Differential Equations I, 2nd Edition", pg.135, pg.166.
